---
description: API development rules
globs: apps/api/**/*.ts
---

This is the Hono API for OpenNG. See CLAUDE.md at the project root for full architecture context.

- Never write code comments
- All routes are generated by the ResourceFactory in apps/api/src/core/factory.ts
- Adding a resource = one config file + one route registration line
- Never connect directly to the DB from route handlers, always use the query helpers in packages/db
